title: Guns 'n' Roses - Lies (expanded by }{eywood)
description:
Guns 'n' Roses
Lies
expanded by }{eywood

Lies was made up from the Live Like A Suicide EP and some new acoustic studio tracks, but some research showed me that at one time there was a release of LLAS that also had Shado of Your Love on it.  I tracked down this recording and added it to the sequencing.  I also put the EP recorded at the Ritz in there, so the first 2/3 of the thing is live with the final 3rd being the studio tracks.

01 It's So Easy
02 Shadow of Your Love
03 Reckless Life
04 Nice Boys
05 Move to the City
06 Mama Kin
07 Knockin' On Heaven's Door
08 Whole Lotta Rosie
09 Patience
10 Used to Love Her
11 You're Crazy
12 One in a Million
